Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodecompare.rst
Summary: Base class for visual shader nodes that perform comparisons.

Inherits: VisualShaderNode < Resource < RefCounted < Object

This class is the base for visual shader nodes that perform comparisons. It provides common functionality for nodes that compare two input values and output a boolean result.

Key Rule: This is an abstract base class and cannot be instantiated directly. Use derived classes like VisualShaderNodeCompare.
