Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodecompare.rst
Summary: Describes the properties of the VisualShaderNodeCompare node, including condition, function, and type.

Property Descriptions
Property: condition (Condition)
Description: Extra condition which is applied if type is set to CTYPE_VECTOR_3D.
Default: 0
Method: set_condition(value: Condition)
Method: get_condition() -> Condition

Property: function (Function)
Description: A comparison function.
Default: 0
Method: set_function(value: Function)
Method: get_function() -> Function

Property: type (ComparisonType)
Description: The type to be used in the comparison.
Default: 0
Method: set_comparison_type(value: ComparisonType)
Method: get_comparison_type() -> ComparisonType